sts in\nthese nearly stoichiometric crystals. However, in addition to an increased AIAO\ntransition temperature, the diffuse signal is seemingly stabilized and remains\nnearly unchanged upon warming to 800 mK. This behavior indicates that both the\nAIAO magnetic order and spin-ice correlations are sensitive to deviations of\nthe Nd stoichiometry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 May 2021 03:04:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 31 Jul 2021 04:48:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 Aug 2021 17:23:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-18"}
