positively associated\nwith urban vitality. This work expands the toolkit of quantitative urban\nmorphology study with new techniques, supporting further studies in the future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 May 2021 08:53:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Jul 2021 13:48:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 21 Aug 2021 02:05:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-24"}
